# “””
mstr_create_devices.py

Replicates a reference File Device across all projects on a MicroStrategy server.

Usage:
python mstr_create_devices.py –reference-device “File Device - ProjectAlpha”

The suffix after the last ’ - ’ is replaced with each project’s name to form
the new device name, e.g.:
Reference : “File Device - ProjectAlpha”
New names : “File Device - ProjectBeta”, “File Device - ProjectGamma”, …

Requirements:
pip install requests

Tested against MicroStrategy Library REST API (September 2025 / v2).
“””

